      "widgets_values": [
        "ℹ️ S-18 Face Pipeline v2 — extract dense landmarks, do a Delaunay warp, then blend the warped result back\n\nChain: LoadImage → N-19 Face Landmarks → N-20 Face Warp → N-21 Face Beauty Blend → PreviewImage. The same source image is wired as both the base plate and the retouched plate here so the scaffold stays self-contained and pack-core-only; replace the N-20 output or the base image with your own retouched face pass in production.\n\nThe LoadImage MASK output is wired into N-21 as a convenient placeholder mask for the demo graph. In a real retouch workflow, replace it with a proper face / skin mask from your own upstream segmentation chain."
